1146
01:07:48.260 --> 01:07:48.520
Yeah.

1147
01:07:48.580 --> 01:07:51.980
They're proximal to that in the gene sequence, with a few

1148
01:07:52.000 --> 01:07:55.960
exceptions. So we don't expect that the molecular glue will

1149
01:07:55.970 --> 01:07:58.280
directly engage many of those fusions.

1150
01:07:58.920 --> 01:08:02.780
But there certainly are some interesting reports of NUP98's activity

