01:10:35.200 --> 01:10:38.940
predominantly chemo proteomics to try and understand

1196
01:10:38.960 --> 01:10:42.560
which types of proteins go together and how these different modalities work.

1197
01:10:43.080 --> 01:10:46.780
So one example is how do we understand how to

